//component
functional
-> Ligth in weight
-> Less functionallity 
-> Presentational Component
-> Can only handle props

Class Component
-> Heavy as compare to functional
-> Lot of functionallity
-> Can handle state & props

// Es5
function add(a,b){
    return a+b
}

// Es6
const add = (a,b) => { return a+b }

